# Appfile — App Store Connect / Apple Developer wiring.
#
# Left blank in the committed file. Real values come from one of two
# places at fastlane invocation time:
#
#   1. Locally — your gitignored `fastlane/.env` file or an
#      `.env.<lane>` variant, picked up by dotenv. Useful while
#      iterating on a lane.
#   2. CI — GitHub Actions secrets exposed as env vars.
#
# Variables Fastlane reads:
#
#   FASTLANE_USER         Apple ID email
#   FASTLANE_TEAM_ID      Apple Developer Team ID
#   FASTLANE_ITC_TEAM_ID  ASC team ID (usually matches Developer team)
#
# Per-lane bundle identifiers are read from the project itself (via
# `PRODUCT_BUNDLE_IDENTIFIER` set in `project.yml`'s targets), so we
# don't restate them here.

# Uncomment + override locally if you need to pin values for a lane:
# app_identifier ENV["CATTY_APP_IDENTIFIER"]
# team_id        ENV["FASTLANE_TEAM_ID"]
# apple_id       ENV["FASTLANE_USER"]
